terrapeer.vui.j3dui.control.actuators
Class TGGeometryPlugin

java.lang.Object
  terrapeer.vui.j3dui.control.actuators.TGGeometryPlugin
Direct Known Subclasses:
AxisAnglePlugin, RotationPlugin, ScalePlugin, TranslationPlugin
public abstract class TGGeometryPlugin
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract base class for personality plugins used by TransformGroupPlugins to define the transform geometry. Also defines the format of the input actuation value.

Unless otherwise noted, all methods are actually used by all TransformGroupPlugins that host this plugin.
